wt.vc.baseline

Interface Baseline

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    _ESIManagedBaseline, _ManagedBaseline, ESIManagedBaseline, ManagedBaseline

    @GenAsPersistable(interfaces={Lockable.class,<error>},
                  extendable=true)
public interface Baseline
    This interface is used to tag a class that represents a Baseline. Asserting this interface allows the class to be associated with Baselineable items.

    Supported API: true

    Extendable: true
